## New template: `generate-db-preview.yml`

This is the part that should run in the **release pipeline**, because `SqlPackage /Action:Script` creates a script for a specific target database. Microsoft documents `DeployScriptPath` and `DeployReportPath` for that action. ([Microsoft Learn][2])

```yaml
parameters:
- name: jobName
  type: string
  default: 'GenerateDbPreview'

- name: jobDisplayName
  type: string
  default: 'Generate DB preview'

- name: deployPool
  type: string

- name: deployAgentName
  type: string

- name: artifactProject
  type: string

- name: artifactDefinitionId
  type: string

- name: artifactBuildId
  type: string

- name: artifactName
  type: string
  default: 'db-drop'

- name: targetConnectionString
  type: string

- name: sqlPackagePath
  type: string
  default: 'SqlPackage'

- name: sqlPackageArgs
  type: string
  default: >
    /p:IgnorePermissions=true
    /p:IgnoreRoleMembership=true
    /p:IgnoreUserSettingsObjects=true
    /p:BlockOnPossibleDataLoss=true
    /p:DropObjectsNotInSource=false

- name: previewArtifactName
  type: string
  default: 'db-preview'

jobs:
- job: ${{ parameters.jobName }}
  displayName: ${{ parameters.jobDisplayName }}

  pool:
    name: ${{ parameters.deployPool }}
    demands:
    - Agent.Name -equals ${{ parameters.deployAgentName }}

  steps:
  - checkout: none

  - task: DownloadPipelineArtifact@2
    displayName: 'Download DB DACPAC artifact'
    inputs:
      project: '${{ parameters.artifactProject }}'
      buildType: 'specific'
      definition: '${{ parameters.artifactDefinitionId }}'
      buildVersionToDownload: 'specific'
      pipelineId: '${{ parameters.artifactBuildId }}'
      artifactName: '${{ parameters.artifactName }}'
      targetPath: '$(Pipeline.Workspace)\dbdrop'

  - powershell: |
      $ErrorActionPreference = 'Stop'

      $dacpac = Get-ChildItem "$(Pipeline.Workspace)\dbdrop" -Recurse -Filter *.dacpac |
                Select-Object -First 1

      if (-not $dacpac) {
        throw "No .dacpac found in downloaded artifact."
      }

      $outDir = "$(Pipeline.Workspace)\db-preview"
      New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path $outDir | Out-Null

      $scriptPath = Join-Path $outDir 'preview-deploy.sql'
      $reportPath = Join-Path $outDir 'deploy-report.xml'

      & "${{ parameters.sqlPackagePath }}" `
        /Action:Script `
        /SourceFile:"$($dacpac.FullName)" `
        /TargetConnectionString:"${{ parameters.targetConnectionString }}" `
        /DeployScriptPath:"$scriptPath" `
        /DeployReportPath:"$reportPath" `
        ${{ parameters.sqlPackageArgs }}

      if ($LASTEXITCODE -ne 0) {
        throw "SqlPackage Script action failed with exit code $LASTEXITCODE"
      }

      Write-Host "Preview script generated at: $scriptPath"
      Write-Host "Deploy report generated at: $reportPath"
    displayName: 'Generate preview SQL and deploy report'

  - task: PublishPipelineArtifact@1
    displayName: 'Publish DB preview artifact'
    inputs:
      targetPath: '$(Pipeline.Workspace)\db-preview'
      artifact: '${{ parameters.previewArtifactName }}'
```

